MeeMee Baby Bath Towel Bath Towel Price: Rs.472

Baby towels can be used for various purposes
column17:
from wiping you baby dry after his bath to covering him up for his nap. These baby bath towels have to be of soft fabric so that they are not harsh on an infant’s skin. The baby bath towel from Mee Mee is made of 100 per cent cotton and they conform to the comfort requisites any parent would put forth. This machine washable Mee Mee Bath Towel comes with the dimensions of 32 x 32 inches.

You can use this Mee Mee Baby Bath Towel for your newborn as the soft fabric will keep them cozy and warm. After giving your tiny tot a bath you can easily snuggle him up with this hooded towel so that he is covered from head to toe. The hood will make sure that your angel will not contract any cold related illnesses by getting exposed to the cold. The visual appeal of this Mee Mee Baby Towel is heightened by the adorable applique embroidery on the hood. You can use this Baby Bath Towel to bundle up your darling before you take her out and even to tuck in your sweetheart for a nice and cozy nap.
